Have had this map laying around for too long. Decided to quickly add an end to it.

~20 seconds; somewhat easy, some jumps and corners can be difficult for new players.

The map's atmosphere was supposed to have an anxiety-type dystopia feel to it. There was a lot more I wanted to do with it, but I couldn't find a good way to do things. I kind of hit a mappers block with this one; regardless, hope you guys like it for what it is.

Made this map because there was someone named justa on GMod bhop with the biggest ego ever. He thought he was the best coder and had the best smoothest gmod bhop server there is put people down that were not in there group, Cat - Vehnex ect. Video here to see what these kids are about. 

 

He had a server called justas cool server with a fake coded RNGFix that he tried to hide from everyone by making his server whitelisted. I made his map after him it Requires CS:S/GMod RNGFix uphill fixes :) that I finally got from a very nice GMod Russian dev named CLazStudio. So happy I finally found some real nice people to play with and not this toxic shit junk loser bullshit. This was not a normal act I had pizza, boxes and stuff send to my house they DDoSed me and made fun of me... enjoy the map! Oh and justa took about 1500 USD dollars from me from tricking me in a fake biding scam with henwi. These kids are sick and need help they only care about cheating records and being assholes. Original map by Kaos_nyrb and SoUlFaThEr
contains 2 courses: kz_antenna and surf_building
Note for servers owners, if using Shavit's timer the end zone is already placed.

kz_cookbook
Original map author unknown
contains 2 courses: kz_cookbook_hard and kz_bridge
notes: Only ported the hard course as having two courses would be impossible in multiplayer without making a complicated filter system and moved the end of kz_cookbook to skip the maze, didn't feel like a crouch hold maze after a 10+ minute kz_course was very fun or enjoyable, it's not removed and you can still get there with noclip.

This is an AWP map I made for a server and I decided to turn it into an FY map. I wanted to add a weapon system inside ammocrates so I tested this version. You don't need to press and to drop the weapons, just get close to the ammocrates and they will open immediately, when you leave their range they will close in a second.

NOTE: I edited the default HL2 ammocrates, but forgot to remove the cubemap tests from them, I will update and remove them soon, as well as the invisible grenade on top of the glass.

Hello! This map used to be originally from a part of Half Life 2 campaign, but I got the idea to PORT it to Counter Strike: Source, because, i like so much this part of the history

The change had some very simple modifications for better balance, in addition, it contains the following:

-2 Sites to plant the C4

-1 Easter Egg (Try to find it!)

RECOMMENDATIONS!
-Mat_specular 0 in console

-Buy night vision, because some parts of the map are very darkness, so, your enemies can hide it!

Hope you like the map!
